  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6609 trading just above the 6606 flip in a PIN regime, dealers are positioned as gamma buyers on any dip toward 6605 support and will aggressively sell into strength at the massive 6610 gamma wall (388B). The recent GEX surge of 35-40% over the past 5 minutes indicates heavy options flow that's reinforcing dealer stabilization behavior, creating a tight trading range between 6605-6615. Key inflection points are the 6590 negative gamma zone where dealer buying accelerates and the 6620 level where the next significant positive gamma wall provides resistance.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect tight range-bound action between 6605-6615 with dealers capping moves in both directions.",
